Author: SemicolonButterfly
Text: Injuries majorly suck, but prompt care (whether at home or through a doc) is worth it. Better to take a rest week now than to keep pushing, have weeks of low quality + painful workouts, and then end by compounding the problem and needing to take months off for a real recovery. (I learned that one the hard way...a couple times)
